data.description: Welcome to your cozy home in the quaint Town of Tappahannock! The private rear yard is a hidden oasis featuring a picturesque flagstone patio, a delightful gazebo for intimate gatherings, and a convenient shed with electricity, perfect for a workshop or extra storage. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the warmth of hardwood floors that flow throughout the home. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting top-of-the-line appliances, including a double wall oven and a propane stove.  The basement reveals a pleasant surprise--a bonus room with a full bathroom, offering versatility for a home office, guest suite, or recreational space. Ascend to the second floor, where a loft awaits, ready to adapt to your needs. Whether you envision a serene office space or a playroom, this area adds an extra layer of flexibility. A separate bedroom provides privacy and a cozy retreat. Location is key, and this property doesn't disappoint. Close to all town amenities, you're just moments away from local shops, dining, and entertainment. Immerse yourself in the vibrant community while enjoying the serenity of your private haven.
